title: Should $CAKE be distributed for christmas?
body:
I think $CAKE should be distributed to community members to celebrate the festive season.
Possibly to encourage stakers both past and present stakers who must have participated in one stake or the other
choices: Yes I agree with you, there should be a christmas bonus
I disagree with you, No christmas bonus
